{
  "id": "adv_card_chs_09_01",
  "title": "白石千紗 1話 凄い衣装が出来ちゃうかも",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_01-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "星見市のテーマパークとのコラボ、ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A collaboration with Hoshimi City's theme park?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。月ストとサニピとの合同ライブでもあるぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. It's also a joint live with Moon Tempest and Sunny Peace.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.5028119405,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.7361452739
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_01-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど……ついに里帰りライブを\nやるっていうことですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… we're finally doing\na homecoming live.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.8762035189,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_01-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "しかも、お姉ちゃんと一緒だなんて……嬉しいです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And together with my sister… I'm so happy!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.4757137299,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 20.4355323156
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_01-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんにいいところ見せられるかな\n楽しみだなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wonder if I can show my sister my good side.\nI'm looking forward to it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.5063316664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.3743986767
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "だが、ちょっと問題もあってな\nまだデザイナーが決まっていないんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But there's a bit of a problem\nWe haven't decided on a designer yet.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.30773201,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.0743986767
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_01-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "デザイナーって、もしかして衣装のですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Designer… could it be for costumes?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.0743986767,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.998865986
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ。あまり時間はないから\n早く見つけないといけないんだが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right. Since we don't have much time‚\nwe need to find someone quickly…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.3321993193,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、千紗は前にも衣装のデザインをしていたな\nあの時の衣装、凄く良かったぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come to think of it‚ Chisa‚ you've designed costumes before.\nThose costumes were really good.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.9023747886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_01-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "はい。ファンのみんなも喜んでくれてました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. All the fans were happy with them too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.9655326527,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.9655326527
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、良かったら今回もやってみないか？\nせっかく沙季とも共演するんだしな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ if you'd like‚ would you try doing it again this time?\nSince you'll be performing with Saki too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.0083446663,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.7083446663
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_01-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "えぇっ、いいんですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eeh‚ is that okay!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.7083446663,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.2324945451
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "千紗のデザインした衣装はファンからも好評だからな\n千紗さえ良ければ、俺が調整を頼んでみるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The costumes you designed were well-received by fans.\nIf you're okay with it‚ I'll try to arrange it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.4991612118,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_01-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "やったぁ……私、頑張ります……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yay… I'll do my best…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.8658278784,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.4390478771
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_01-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "どんな衣装を作ろうかなぁ\n作るからにはいいものを作りたいから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wonder what kind of costume I should make~\nSince I'm making it‚ I want to make something good…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_01-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "ライブに参加するみんなにどんな衣装がいいか\nまずは確認しなくっちゃ……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I should first check with everyone participating in the live\nwhat kind of costumes they'd prefer…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "まだ時間はあるからゆっくり考えてくれていいぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We still have time‚ so take your time thinking about it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.3894901595,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.3894901595
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_01-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうですよね\n嬉しくてちょっと舞い上がっちゃいました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-yes‚ that's right.\nI got a little carried away because I was so happy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.4999938965,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.9077213925
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_01-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "作るならやっぱり豪華なものにした方がいいのかな\n星見市の要素も入れなくっちゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I’m making it‚ I guess it should be luxurious.\nI need to include elements of Hoshimi City too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.9333272298,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 104.8188100816
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_01-chs013.m4a",
      "text": "いろいろアイデアが浮かんできます！\n素敵な衣装にしてみせますね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Various ideas are coming to mind!\nI'll make a wonderful costume!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.4999938965,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。どんな衣装が出来上がるのか\n楽しみにしているよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. I'm looking forward to seeing\nwhat kind of costume you create.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.2374496144,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Several days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.8707829477,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1395.8776155000123,
          "startTime": 117.2666605632
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.9999938965
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.9999938965
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "おはよう、千紗",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning‚ Chisa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.837450123,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119.4707834563
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_01-chs014.m4a",
      "text": "ひゃっ……お、おはようございます！\nいたんですね、{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hya… G-good morning!\nYou were here‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.4571554354,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "ええっと、机の上がやけに\n散らかっているようだが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ the desk seems\nquite messy…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.6666605632,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.9699941637
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
